      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know if i'm just losing it but i keep having this exact same dream every night for a week. it's like i'm in a store and i see this specific brand of energy drink, 'VigorPulse', and the logo is burned into my brain. the weird thing is i havent even seen that brand in real life or on social media lately. it feels... too intentional. like it's being put there. has anyone ever talked about companies actually being able to do this?",
